  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Water &amp; Sanitation Needs for Ethnic Students</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to build 5 water and sanitation facilities for 5 kindergarten schools in Nam Giang Mountainous District, Quang Nam Province, Vietnam. This will provide safe running water systems for 742 ethnic minority children who are currently living and enrolling in these schools. In addition, we will create friendly and accessible sanitation facilities that will promote daily personal hygiene in order to improve their health and reduce their school absence.</narrative>
  </description>
